{"tid":104537,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經] 應否削減大學學額?","createTime":"2017-02-02T07:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T08:03:46.000Z","uid":75870,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f59d19cbbc7b38c122332200e61ce6e1edade5de","tid":104537,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"削減學額能提升大學生議價能力，<br />\n但削減後新一代整體教育水平會隨之下降。<br />\n<br />\n兩者如何平衡？<br />\n<br />\n贊成削減：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對削減：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我是反對的，因為覺得削減左都唔會提升到議價能力。反正神科／專科會跟據供求調節（如控制收生／牌照試既合格率），最大化自己係市場既議價能力。<br />\n<br />\n留低澎漲供應既都只會係非神科／專科，對工作能力無重要影響。即使只有少部份人擁有如此既學位亦唔會令佢地有大優勢。<br />\n<br />\n不削減學位可以令全民教育水平提高，而且與大學學位眨值無直接／重要關係。<br />\n<br />\n結論：贊成削減既都係讀緊乞食科但又想要優越感既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1a6009603945c6ecbcb5f6a0182aaa9125ed8c","tid":104537,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"已經變世紀經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d7d943f129a74bab8eb3fe6157321067ca1df1","tid":104537,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"個個都係大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}